---
title: 完整的后端中间件链
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 客户端
    participant ASGI as ASGI Server (uvicorn)
    participant RLM as RequestLogMiddleware
    participant RPM as RoutePermissionMiddleware
    participant SAM as StaticAuthMiddleware
    participant CORS as CORSMiddleware
    participant Route as 业务路由
    participant DB as MySQL

    Client->>ASGI: HTTP Request
    ASGI->>RLM: 中间件 1: 请求日志
    Note over RLM: 记录请求体、URL、操作者
    RLM->>RPM: 中间件 2: 路由权限
    Note over RPM: 白名单放行 → 检查 require_auth → 检查角色/用户权限
    RPM->>SAM: 中间件 3: 静态文件鉴权
    Note over SAM: 仅检查挂载路径的静态文件
    SAM->>CORS: 中间件 4: 跨域
    CORS->>Route: 到达业务路由
    Route->>DB: 业务处理
    DB-->>Route: 结果
    Route-->>CORS: api_response()
    CORS-->>SAM: 响应
    SAM-->>RPM: 响应
    RPM-->>RLM: 响应
    RLM-->>ASGI: 响应
    ASGI-->>Client: 最终响应